OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,FHowever, it comes two years after the
OL,7,FStates of Jersey approved a
OL,8,Flegislative tweak to allow the
OL,9,Fauthorities to share more information
OL,10,Fabout islanders with companies that
OL,11,Fcomplete credit checks.
OL,13,FThe Jersey Consumer Council is now
OL,14,Fpushing for answers as to why the
OL,15,Fproblem persists.
OL,17,FMaria Hoyles, who lives in Jersey,
OL,18,Fsays: "For two years, I've been trying
OL,19,Fto get a credit card. I went to my
OL,20,Fbank, which I've been banking with for
OL,21,F52 years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
