OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,F"They said they were not issuing
OL,7,Fcredit cards at the moment - even
OL,8,Fthough I have three savings accounts
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,F"At the moment, I have to use either a
OL,12,Fdebit card or cash. It would be nice
OL,13,Fto have one credit card to pay for
OL,14,Fholidays or stays in hotels, or even
OL,15,Fjust for local shopping.
OL,17,F"Jersey is supposed to be a finance
OL,18,Fcentre, and yet Jersey residents can't
OL,19,Fget a credit card, which is very
OL,20,Funfair."
