OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,FCarl Walker, Chair of Jersey's
OL,7,FConsumer Council, says islanders will
OL,8,Fcontinue to face problems unless the
OL,9,FStates passes new legislation.
OL,11,FHe explains: "Our understanding is
OL,12,Fthat there have been some legal issues
OL,13,Fin terms of access to data, and who
OL,14,Fmight have access by default.
OL,16,F"That has been sorted, and now we need
OL,17,Fthe officers behind this scheme to get
OL,18,Fit over the line.
