OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,F"Consumers on a daily basis are still
OL,7,Fcontacting us, saying they've been
OL,8,Fturned down for credit card
OL,9,Fapplications. We're worried that this
OL,10,Fmay escalate if it gets towards home
OL,11,Floans, car loans, and mortgages. Who
OL,12,Fknows where it might lead?
OL,14,F"There's a fundamental issue at the
OL,15,Fcore of it, and there's a window of
OL,16,Fopportunity to sort it, and that is
OL,17,Fnow."
