OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,FDeputy Ian Gorst, Jersey's Minister
OL,7,Ffor Financial Services, says credit
OL,8,Fcards are still available for
OL,9,Fislanders from several banks.
OL,11,FHe explains: "While we welcome more UK
OL,12,Fproviders operating in Jersey, these
OL,13,Fdecisions remain commercial and are
OL,14,Fultimately for businesses to make.
