OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,F"We have been working to resolve a
OL,7,Flegal issue that has prevented the
OL,8,Fsupply of data to Credit Reference
OL,9,FAgencies. The necessary legislative
OL,10,Fdrafting to remove this barrier has
OL,11,Fcommenced, and the draft law will be
OL,12,Fbrought to the States Assembly as soon
OL,13,Fas possible.
