OL,3,CChannel Islanders declined credit
OL,4,Ccards as they do not have UK addresses
OL,6,F"Access to credit cards depends on
OL,7,Fresponsible lending practices and
OL,8,Findividual creditworthiness. Providers
OL,9,Fmust ensure credit is extended only to
OL,10,Fthose with the ability to repay. This
OL,11,Fmay ultimately result in some
OL,12,FIslanders having their applications
OL,13,Ffor cards rejected."
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the States of Guernsey has
OL,16,Fbeen working to give credit reference
OL,17,Fagencies access to the island's
OL,18,Felectoral roll.
